Makeup for Miss Grand International @_rachelgupta 🧿

Still absorbing this! So grateful for the chance to do the makeup for the beautiful Rachel Gupta, Miss Grand International! 👑

Feeling incredibly grateful for the opportunity.
Thank you for trusting me with your beauty. Here’s to empowering women and celebrating beauty in all its forms!
This experience has truly been a DREAM COME TRUE. Thank you for allowing me to be a part of your journey. Feeling blessed! 🙏🏻

SPECIALLY and ETERNALLY  THANKFUL to @sakshi.404 @socialfire_co for making this happen for me 🙏🏻

#makeupbymuskan #missgrandinternal2024 
 #Gratitude #MakeupMagic” #dreamscometrue #growth #delhimakeupartist

Glammed the badminton legend not once but twice 🥹 and it’s always an honor to be called back by someone so humble and kind. 
We went for a soft, radiant look glowing skin, warm-toned eyes, and a mauve lip that complements her grace perfectly. ✨

@nehwalsaina working with you is truly a joy hoping for many more to come! 🙏🏻❤️

As makeup artists, we’re here to bring your vision to life not replace it.
It’s your day, your face, your moment. 💍
They can guide and suggest, but they should never override your choices.

Few tips before you book your MUA:

1.Have a clear conversation about your style, comfort, and expectations.

2.Make sure they understand your vision, not just their own aesthetic.

3.Ask if they’re willing to adapt it’s important you feel heard and seen.

At the end of the day, the bride should feel like herself just elevated.
